{
  "stem": "13096.5",
  "chunk_idx": 15,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "So the next day, we saw around there were no Germans.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "One of the other friends, that she was with us, that she was speaking Spanish.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And her name is Stella [NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And after that, she marry very well.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And she was leaving in Nice.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "But now she die all the same from natural causes.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "So we were assigned to go around in the-- you know-- in the neighborhood to-- to something to eat.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "But the Germans have stayed there previously in those big buildings, surely we find something.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Eventually, we find some pieces of bread, some tins of sardines.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But it was so heavy, we had no strength to take it.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "If it was mild, we could walk in the whole day we were gone to find food for the other people staying in our hut.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "What we did, we find a piece of plank.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And we find a piece of coal.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "We tie it up and we make like a sledge to bring to the place where the other people were staying.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And like that, we know-- we were-- we were eating and drinking water and keeping the thing alive.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "We had plenty of coal.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "We find not just into the hut-- was a big deposit of coal.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And we were just keeping alive, you know, the fire day and night and eating whatever we find.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "If I tell you the things we saw in those apartments from the Germans, unbelievable.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "There was plenty of Persian carpet, maybe they have taken from the Jewish.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "You see jewelry.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "We see anything.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "But we were not too interested.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "What we are looking is food.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "Whatever find a piece of sardine, and piece this and piece that, we were taking that to the barracks.",
      "word_count": 19
    }
  ],
